        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Reducing Racial and Ethnic Disparities in the Juvenile Justice System Act of 2022</b></p> <p>This bill modifies provisions under the Juvenile Justice and Delinquency Prevention Program in order to more specifically address racial and ethnic disparities with respect to arrests, secure detentions, and other decision points.</p>]]></text>
